definitions.definition: To transfer data to a computer on a network , especially to a server on the Internet .
examples: You will have to convert your photograph to a jpg format if you wish to upload it.

definitions.definition: To transfer jurisdiction and responsibility of a government asset or service to a higher level of government.

main_definition: ( transitive , intransitive , computing ) To transfer data to a computer on a network , especially to a server on the Internet .
secondary_definitions: ( Canada ) To transfer jurisdiction and responsibility of a government asset or service to a higher level of government.
